<?oxygen NVDLSchema="../../../../../../../oxygen/samples/nvdl/xhtml-xforms-11-orbeon.nvdl"?>
<div 
	xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" 
	xmlns:xforms="http://www.w3.org/2002/xforms" 
	xmlns:ev="http://www.w3.org/2001/xml-events"
	xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">

	<p>The study information assists us in curating your data – especially if your data is not yet published. If you do not have time to complete the questionnaire, the study curator will try to derive the answers from the publications you’ve provided.
	</p>
	
	<p>You can copy study info from another study for which you have administrator/creator rights. If you copy information from an existing questionnaire it will overwrite any answer you’ve given, so be sure to update any information that differs from the copied study info.
	</p>
	
	<p>When you enter new information, be sure to save your changes. 
	</p>

	<xforms:group ref="instance('ins-control')/copy-answers-control">
	<p>

		<span id="studies-to-copy-answers-from-menu-container">
		<xforms:select1 ref="instance('ins-control')/href-to-copy-study-info-from">
			<xforms:label>Copy answers from another study?</xforms:label>
			
			<xforms:item>
				<xforms:label>Select...</xforms:label>
			    <xforms:value></xforms:value>
			</xforms:item>
		
           	<xforms:itemset nodeset="xxforms:sort(instance('ins-study-feed')/atom:entry[atom:id!=instance('ins-study-entry')/atom:id], atom:published, 'text', 'ascending')">
           		<xforms:label ref="concat(atom:title, ' (', manta:id, ')')"/>
           		<xforms:value ref="atom:link[@rel='http://www.cggh.org/2010/chassis/terms/studyInfo']/@href"/>
           	</xforms:itemset>
		</xforms:select1>
		</span>

		<span id="copy-answers-button-container">
		<xforms:trigger ref="instance('ins-control')/copy-answers-trigger">
			<xforms:label>Copy answers</xforms:label>
			<xforms:action ev:event="DOMActivate">
				<xforms:send submission="sub-copy-answers" />
			</xforms:action>
		</xforms:trigger>
		</span>
		
	</p>
	</xforms:group>


     <p>
     	<span class="study-info-save-changes-button-container">
         <xforms:submit submission="sub-put-sq-study-info-entry">
             <xforms:label>Save changes</xforms:label>
         </xforms:submit>
     	</span>
     </p>
	
	<xi:include href="../../../common/includes/study/study-info-input.xml" />
	
     <p>
     	<span class="study-info-save-changes-button-container">
         <xforms:submit submission="sub-put-sq-study-info-entry">
             <xforms:label>Save changes</xforms:label>
         </xforms:submit>
     	</span>
     </p>


</div>